page.title: 09SERVICES -GARAGES IN HARBURY
page.content: There are four garages in Harbury. They are the Bull Ring Garage owned by Mr. David Holyoake, the Fosse Garage owned by Mr. Martin Shepherd and Mill Street Garage and Dovehouse Auto Services owned by Mrs. F Byron and Mr. E Buckle. 7 people, 7 people, l person and 3 people work in each of the garages respectively. The Bull Ring Garage, Fosse Garage and Dovehouse Auto Services do repairs. The two garages which sell petrol are Mill Street Garage and the Fosse Garage, both selling 2,3, and 4 star petrol.
